\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {2}{\ignorespaces Cross-domain evaluation loss matrix at Pythia-410M, step 2,000 (freeze=4, seed=42). Rows are specialists; columns are evaluation domains. The diagonal entries (own-domain performance) are lower than off-diagonal (cross-domain), confirming that each specialist has diverged in a complementary direction. The MoE router recovers diagonal performance across all domains simultaneously. Color scale: green indicates lower loss (better performance), red indicates higher loss.}}{9}{figure.caption.36}\protected@file@percent }
