\newlabel{fig:routerdist}{{5}{16}{Learned gate weight distributions for all three domain evaluation sets (Pythia-410M, freeze=4, seed=42). Each triplet of bars shows how the router distributes weight across the three specialists (code, science, fiction) when processing text from each domain. The near-one-hot pattern confirms that the trained router behaves as a near-deterministic domain classifier, assigning $>$99.7\% weight to the correct specialist}{figure.caption.50}{}}
